Package no.uio.duo

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BitstreamIterator
    Convenience class to allow us to iterate through all bitstreams in an item, retrieving both the bitstream and the bundle within which we are viewing it.
    CristinBundleVersioningStrategy
    This versioning strategy does nothing, it simply returns leaving all the bundles alone, as the versioning will be handled by the ORE ingester
    CristinIngestFilter
    Implementation of the IngestFilter which determines whether the incoming harvest record should be accepted or not
    CristinIngestionWorkflow
    Implementation of the Harveter's IngestionWorkflow, providing hooks for the OAI-PMH harvesting features.
    CristinMetadataRemover
    Implementation of the MetadataRemover interface, which allows us to selectively clear old metadata before the item is updated
    CristinOAIDCCrosswalk
    A crosswalk to be used with the CRISTIN oai_dc document.
    CristinOREImporter
    Importer which implements both the standard DSpace IngestionCrosswalk and the more advanced OAIConfigurableCrosswalk.
    DeduplicateCristinIds
    Command line script to detect when two cristin IDs are present in the dataset and to output a human readable list of the matches.
    DSpace18FixedDispatcher Deprecated
    DuoConstants  
    DuoEntryDisseminator
    Implementation of the SwordEntryDisseminator which can provide the embedded metadata for StudentWeb alongside a Dublin Core version of the metadata
    DuoEventConsumer
    Event consumer for Duo which responds to Item Installs and Modify (and potentially Modify_Metadata too).
    DuoState
    Convenience class for representing the event state of an item in DSpace
    DuoStateCurationTask
    Curation task which allows the DuoState method synchroniseItemState to be run from the user interface or the command line
    FileManager
    Class to provide file and bundle management utilities for the Duo module
    FSBagItIngester
    Sword Content Ingester to deal with the BagIt format used by the StudentWeb/FS integration
    FSEntryIngester
    Implementation of the SwordEntryIngester interface which takes the FS metadata as embedded in an atom entry and adds it to an existing object
    FSRestrictionManager
    Class to apply restriction rules to items coming from StudentWeb
    IncomingBitstream
    Entity class to represent a bitstream being retrieved from Cristin
    MetadataManager
    Class for providing utilities for Metadata management in the Duo module
    NumberChecker  
    TraverseDSpace
    Utility base class for scripts that want to be able to traverse the whole of DSpace, or parts of it.
    URNGenerator
    Command line script to enhance the metadata of an item with a URN retrieved from the National Library and the urls of all the bitstreams associated with an item
    WorkflowManagerWrapper
    Wraper class providing an abstraction over the DSpace workflow manager.
    XmlUIBitstreamReorder
    Processing action to handle the change of bitstream orders in the customisable workflow
    XmlUIBitstreamReorderUI
    XMLUI Action to provide a bitstream reorder UI
    XmlUICollectionAssignment
    Processing action to handle the assignment of an item to multiple collections
    XmlUICollectionAssignmentUI
    XMLUI Action to provide a Collection assignment workflow stage
    XmlUICollectionAssignmentUI.TreeNode
    Private class to represent the tree structure of communities & collections.

    Exception Description
    DuoException
